Invocation Name: delightful dishes
des:
Delightful Dishes is an Alexa cooking skill with meals for every time of day. Simply say to Alexa, 'Open Delightful Dishes.' Next, you'll be prompted to choose a meal for breakfast, lunch, dinner, or a snack. From there, Alexa will be your sous chef, guiding you as you cook your very own delightful dish.

Food Safety Information: Please consult a healthcare professional or refer to government guidelines if you have concerns about allergies, dietary restrictions, or food safety and handling.
